./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:242:   Native Image must always work; partial dynamic-access coverage with a\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:259:    Improved -- no --> Keep{keep-tests-without-dynamic-access<br/>AND tests changed since start<br/>AND prompt_iterations > 0}\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:307:The `--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access` flag is the only mechanism for\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:322:| `prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md` | Per-class prompt template. |\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:330:1. The dynamic-access report at the end of Phase 2 contains zero uncovered\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:333:   `--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access` was set and tests changed.\nforge/utility_scripts/large_library_progress.py:246:        \"\"\"Record aggregate dynamic-access coverage.\"\"\"\nforge/tests/test_dynamic_access_iterative_strategy.py:42:            \"[dynamic-access] ===================================================================================\\n\"\nforge/tests/test_dynamic_access_iterative_strategy.py:43:            \"[dynamic-access] Progress after org.example.SomeClass: \"\nforge/tests/test_dynamic_access_iterative_strategy.py:45:            \"[dynamic-access] ===================================================================================\",\nforge/tests/test_dynamic_access_iterative_strategy.py:498:                    \"prompts\": {\"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"unused\"},\nforge/tests/test_dynamic_access_iterative_strategy.py:592:                \"prompts\": {\"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"unused\"},\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/ReadmeBadgeSummarySupport.java:509:                        \"dynamic-access\",\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org.graalvm.internal.tck.gradle:36:        // Restrict cacheability to the dynamic-access reporting lane.\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org.graalvm.inte